{
  "message": "test(conformance): add string and shape/stride adversarial cases (+24)\n\nString adversarial edge cases (12 cases):\n- str_empty_string_lower: empty string handling\n- str_whitespace_only_strip: whitespace-only strings\n- str_find_empty_substr: finding empty substring\n- str_find_not_found: substring not present\n- str_replace_empty_old: replacing empty string\n- str_split_empty_sep: splitting on empty separator\n- str_zfill_already_wider: zfill when already wider\n- str_center_zero_width: center with zero width\n- str_count_overlapping: non-overlapping count semantics\n- str_multiply_by_zero/negative: zero/negative multiplier\n- str_isdigit_empty: isdigit on empty string\n\nShape/stride adversarial edge cases (12 cases):\n- sce_empty_shape: scalar broadcast\n- sce_zero_dim_broadcast: broadcasting with zero dimension\n- sce_incompatible_shapes: incompatible broadcast error\n- sce_reshape_to_zero_dim: reshaping to zero dimensions\n- sce_reshape_infer_negative: -1 dimension inference\n- sce_reshape_multiple_negatives: multiple -1 error\n- sce_transpose_empty: transposing empty array\n- sce_squeeze_no_ones: squeeze when no 1-dims\n- sce_expand_dims_negative_axis: negative axis handling\n- sce_strides_zero_itemsize: zero itemsize edge case\n- sce_scalar_broadcast: scalar to nd broadcast\n- sce_ravel_fortran_order: F-order flattening\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.5 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
